---
const pageTitle = "Start Making Money Online With a Simple Beginner-Friendly System";
const pageDescription =
  "Free guide for beginners who want a simple way to start building income online without complicated tools or hype.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />

    <meta property="og:title" content={pageTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={pageDescription} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0b1020;
        --bg-soft: #121933;
        --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        --text: #f5f7ff;
        --muted: #b8c0df;
        --accent: #6ee7b7;
        --accent-dark: #10b981;
        --cta: #ffd166;
        --cta-hover: #ffbf3c;
        --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        --radius: 20px;
        --max: 1140px;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, #1b2550 0%, transparent 35%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, #103c38 0%, transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #09101e 0%, #0b1020 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .container {
        width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 2rem));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 40px 0 70px;
      }

      .topbar {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 10px 16px;
        background: rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.25);
        color: #d6ffef;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        gap: 28px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .hero-copy,
      .hero-form {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .hero-copy {
        padding: 38px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .subheadline {
        margin: 0 0 22px;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 58ch;
      }

      .bullets {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .bullets li {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: flex-start;
        color: #eef2ff;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .check {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        display: inline-grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid rgba(110, 231, 183, 0.25);
        color: var(--accent);
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .primary-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 16px 22px;
        background: var(--cta);
        color: #151515;
        border-radius: 14px;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1rem;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.22);
        transition:
          transform 0.18s ease,
          background 0.18s ease;
      }

      .primary-btn:hover {
        background: var(--cta-hover);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .micro-note {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .hero-form {
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .form-card-title {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .form-card-text {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .form-wrap {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      label {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #dce4ff;
      }

      input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 15px 16px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        background: rgba(10, 16, 32, 0.75);
        color: white;
        font-size: 1rem;
        outline: none;
      }

      input::placeholder {
        color: #8f99bb;
      }

      input:focus {
        border-color: rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.6);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.12);
      }

      button[type="submit"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cta) 0%, #ffc44d 100%);
        color: #111;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition:
          transform 0.18s ease,
          filter 0.18s ease;
      }

      button[type="submit"]:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        filter: brightness(1.02);
      }

      .privacy-note {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .trust-strip {
        margin-top: 18px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .trust-item {
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: #e5ebff;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .section {
        padding: 0 0 70px;
      }

      .section-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: 34px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .section-title {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.8vw, 2.5rem);
      }

      .section-subtitle {
        margin: 0 0 26px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 70ch;
      }

      .three-col {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .info-box {
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(10, 16, 32, 0.48);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .info-box h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.08rem;
      }

      .info-box p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .who-wrap {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .who-box {
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(10, 16, 32, 0.48);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .who-box h3 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .who-box ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .final-cta {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .final-cta p {
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 60ch;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 0 0 40px;
      }

      .footer p {
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
        color: #98a3c7;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      @media (max-width: 920px) {
        .hero-grid,
        .three-col,
        .who-wrap {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .hero-copy,
        .hero-form,
        .section-card {
          padding: 24px;
        }

        .hero {
          padding-top: 24px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="topbar">
            <div class="badge">Free Beginner Guide • Simple Online Income System</div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-copy">
              <span class="eyebrow">Beginner-Friendly • No Hype • Simple Steps</span>
              <h1>Start Making Money Online With a Simple System You Can Actually Follow</h1>
              <p class="subheadline">
                Download this free guide and learn a clear, beginner-friendly approach
                to building online income without getting lost in complicated tools,
                endless courses, or confusing strategies.
              </p>

              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>
                  <span class="check">✓</span>
                  <span>Discover the simple 3-part model behind most successful online income systems.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="check">✓</span>
                  <span>Learn what beginners usually do wrong and how to avoid wasting time.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="check">✓</span>
                  <span>See how to start building an audience and a list you can grow long-term.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="check">✓</span>
                  <span>Get a practical starting point even if you are still figuring everything out.</span>
                </li>
              </ul>

              <div class="cta-row">
                <a class="primary-btn" href="#optin">Get Instant Access</a>
                <span class="micro-note">Free guide. Simple strategy. Beginner-friendly.</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <aside class="hero-form" id="optin">
              <h2 class="form-card-title">Get the Free Guide</h2>
              <p class="form-card-text">
                Enter your best email below and I’ll send you the free guide that breaks
                down a simple path to getting started online.
              </p>

              <!-- Replace the action URL with your autoresponder form endpoint -->
              <div class="form-wrap">
  <a href="https://a8a5-darwin.systeme.io/36e6d282" class="cta-btn">
    Get Instant Access
  </a>
</div>
              >
                <div>
                  <label for="name">First Name</label>
                  <input
                    id="name"
                    name="name"
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Your first name"
                    autocomplete="given-name"
                    required
                  />
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                  <input
                    id="email"
                    name="email"
                    type="email"
                    placeholder="Your best email address"
                    autocomplete="email"
                    required
                  />
                </div>

                <!-- Optional hidden fields for your autoresponder -->
                <!-- <input type="hidden" name="tag" value="bridge-page-dailyads" /> -->
                <!-- <input type="hidden" name="source" value="dailyads" /> -->

                <button type="submit">Send Me the Free Guide</button>
              </form>

              <p class="privacy-note">
                We respect your privacy. You can unsubscribe at any time with one click.
              </p>

              <div class="trust-strip">
                <div class="trust-item">No complicated tech setup required to understand this.</div>
                <div class="trust-item">Designed for beginners who want a simple starting point.</div>
                <div class="trust-item">Clear, practical, and focused on long-term list building.</div>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-card">
            <h2 class="section-title">What You’ll Learn Inside</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              This is not another vague “make money online” ebook. It is a practical,
              simplified overview designed to help you understand what really matters first.
            </p>

            <div class="three-col">
              <div class="info-box">
                <h3>The Simple Online Income Model</h3>
                <p>
                  Understand the core pieces behind building online income without
                  overcomplicating the process.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="info-box">
                <h3>Why Most Beginners Stay Stuck</h3>
                <p>
                  Learn the common mistakes that keep people jumping from method to method
                  without real progress.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="info-box">
                <h3>How to Start the Smart Way</h3>
                <p>
                  See a cleaner path to getting traction by focusing on simplicity,
                  consistency, and list building.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-card">
            <h2 class="section-title">Who This Is For</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
              This guide is for people who want a realistic way to begin online without
              pretending that instant results are normal.
            </p>

            <div class="who-wrap">
              <div class="who-box">
                <h3>This is for you if…</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>You want to start making money online but feel overwhelmed.</li>
                  <li>You are tired of hearing hype and want a simpler path.</li>
                  <li>You want to build something long-term instead of chasing random offers.</li>
                  <li>You are willing to learn a basic system and apply it consistently.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="who-box">
                <h3>This is not for you if…</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>You are looking for a magic button or instant riches.</li>
                  <li>You do not want to build an audience or an email list.</li>
                  <li>You expect results without testing, learning, or improving.</li>
                  <li>You only want hype instead of a usable process.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-card final-cta">
            <h2 class="section-title">Ready to Get the Free Guide?</h2>
            <p>
              Get instant access and start with a clear, beginner-friendly framework
              you can understand quickly and build on over time.
            </p>
            <a class="primary-btn" href="#optin">Yes, Send Me the Guide</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <p>
          This page is for educational and informational purposes only. Results are not
          guaranteed and will vary based on effort, consistency, skill, and market factors.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>